{"code":200,"msg":"success","data":[{"id":253,"createTime":"2019-06-03 10:34:07","topicId":null,"tagId":61,"rule":4,"weight":1,"sort":1,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p style=\"line-height:24px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">痫性发作与惊厥</span></strong></p><table><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9); border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、病因诱因：特发性（癫痫）、症状性（各种心脑血管疾病及中毒、代谢障碍）</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、主要症状特点：惊厥发作形式（全身抽搐、持续性强直性痉挛、局限性抽搐）、发作时间、持续时间、缓解因素？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、伴随症状：是否伴发热、血压增高、脑膜刺激征、剧烈头痛、意识丧失？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、全身状态：发病以来饮食、睡眠、大小便及体重变化</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、诊疗经过：发病以来是否到医院检查过，曾做过哪些检查和治疗？（颅脑CT、MRI、脑电图、血生化）治疗是否有效？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、相关病史：(1)有无药物过敏史、手术史</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">(2)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">既往有无类似病史？有无脑部外伤史？有无脑部疾病、感染性疾病、心血管疾病史、寄生虫、职业病？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"","topic":null,"options":[],"tags":[{"id":299,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-01 16:04:42","updateTime":"2019-06-01 16:04:42","name":"痫性发作与惊厥","questionCnt":1,"tagTypeId":19},{"id":61,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-01 13:47:51","updateTime":"2019-06-01 13:47:51","name":"痫性发作与惊厥","questionCnt":1,"tagTypeId":15}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null}]}